{
  "stem": "443.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first sign of trouble I remember when I was away from home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sent away to yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "15.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there came an order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only way the orders came those days was announced through a-- a drum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There used to come a drummer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He used to go from street to street and drum that he has news to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody gather around this man, and he was telling everybody whatever news there was to be told.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a time that he said that the school is going to be closed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we already knew that something is brewing, some-- some kind of trouble is-- is-- is on its way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's when they evacuated the school, and we went home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my way home, the train wasn't going all the way through to my town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it stopped off at my uncle's house, by the name of-- the name-- the city's names, the little small city, was named Krolla Nadkara.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I slept over there over the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the following morning, there was another train going a little further.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, trains didn't go like over here, from one end to the other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had few hours of train here, a few hours of train there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And then I went home, and I stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't that I could go to another school, because the schools were closed already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's when trouble started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we tried to help out my grandfather's store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother didn't have a store then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What we did, we-- we got a concession of the bathhouse from the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, those days, people didn't have water connections in the house or bathrooms in the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
